data.description: Check out this beautifully maintained 1-bedroom condo in the heart of downtown Norfolk. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, museums, the Scope, light rail, night life and much more that Grandy St and Downtown Norfolk has to offer. Building with private access and assigned covered parking for two cars as well on street city permitted parking. This condo has an open floor plan to spacious kitchen with a breakfast bar and living room with gas fireplace. Come and enjoy the city life at your fingertips.
